#. <section class="sutta" id="an5.37"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.37:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.37:0.2"
msgid "4. Sumanavagga"
msgstr "4. With Sumanā"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.37:0.3"
msgid "37. Bhojanasutta"
msgstr "37. Food"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli3.42"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an5.37:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Bhojanaṃ, bhikkhave, dadamāno dāyako paṭiggāhakānaṃ pañca ṭhānāni deti."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, when a giver gives food, they give the recipients five things."

msgctxt "an5.37:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

#. VAR: paṭibhānaṃ → paṭibhāṇaṃ (bj, s1-3)
msgctxt "an5.37:1.3"
msgid "Āyuṃ deti, vaṇṇaṃ deti, sukhaṃ deti, balaṃ deti, paṭibhānaṃ deti."
msgstr "Long life, beauty, happiness, strength, and inspiration."

msgctxt "an5.37:1.4"
msgid "Āyuṃ kho pana datvā āyussa bhāgī hoti dibbassa vā mānusassa vā;"
msgstr "Giving long life, they have long life as a god or human."

msgctxt "an5.37:1.5"
msgid "vaṇṇaṃ datvā vaṇṇassa bhāgī hoti dibbassa vā mānusassa vā;"
msgstr "Giving beauty, they have beauty as a god or human."

msgctxt "an5.37:1.6"
msgid "sukhaṃ datvā sukhassa bhāgī hoti dibbassa vā mānusassa vā;"
msgstr "Giving happiness, they have happiness as a god or human."

msgctxt "an5.37:1.7"
msgid "balaṃ datvā balassa bhāgī hoti dibbassa vā mānusassa vā;"
msgstr "Giving strength, they have strength as a god or human."

msgctxt "an5.37:1.8"
msgid "paṭibhānaṃ datvā paṭibhānassa bhāgī hoti dibbassa vā mānusassa vā."
msgstr "Giving inspiration, they have inspiration as a god or human."

msgctxt "an5.37:1.9"
msgid ""
"Bhojanaṃ, bhikkhave, dadamāno dāyako paṭiggāhakānaṃ imāni pañca ṭhānāni "
"detīti."
msgstr "When a giver gives food, they give the recipients five things."

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an5.37:2.1"
msgid "Āyudo balado dhīro,"
msgstr "A wise person is a giver of life, strength,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.37:2.2"
msgid "vaṇṇado paṭibhānado;"
msgstr "beauty, and inspiration."

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.37:2.3"
msgid "Sukhassa dātā medhāvī,"
msgstr "An intelligent giver of happiness"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.37:2.4"
msgid "sukhaṃ so adhigacchati."
msgstr "gains happiness in return."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an5.37:3.1"
msgid "Āyuṃ datvā balaṃ vaṇṇaṃ,"
msgstr "Giving life, strength, beauty,"

#. <br>
#. VAR: paṭibhānakaṃ → paṭibhāṇakaṃ (bj) | paṭibhānado (s1-3, km, pts1, mr)
msgctxt "an5.37:3.2"
msgid "sukhañca paṭibhānakaṃ;"
msgstr "happiness, and inspiration,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.37:3.3"
msgid "Dīghāyu yasavā hoti,"
msgstr "they’re long-lived and famous"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.37:3.4"
msgid "yattha yatthūpapajjatī”ti."
msgstr "wherever they’re reborn.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.37:3.5"
msgid "Sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""
